data.description: Nice three bedroom, single story home at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. Fresh paint throughout interior. Living room has fireplace, vaulted ceiling and large, sunny entry. Efficient kitchen with abundant cabinets and counter space, breakfast bar, plus large dining area. Spacious master bedroom with vaulted ceiling, master bath has shower and tub. Medium sized back yard with large side yard and shed. Home has a solar lease with SunRun, which is an easy transfer - monthly payment is $101. It also has a water softener and purifier system! *Buyer to verify schools*
